877
01:07:12,680 --> 01:07:15,319
In the bathroom, do you
remember what happened?

878
01:07:15,320 --> 01:07:18,126
Look, Karina and I aced
the practice test, OK?

879
01:07:19,800 --> 01:07:21,759
