can we go somewhere private?

902
01:08:47,880 --> 01:08:49,764
- Gosh.
- There's not too many people.

903
01:08:51,200 --> 01:08:52,686
But it's purple.

904
01:08:54,480 --> 01:08:57,119
It is purple. Get on.

905
01:08:57,120 --> 01:09:00,961
