It's right here then. All right?

909
01:09:08,920 --> 01:09:10,239
Zooey, all right.

910
01:09:10,240 --> 01:09:11,851
- Whoa. OK?
- OK.

911
01:09:13,360 --> 01:09:14,919
- Good.
- Easy, please.

912
01:09:14,920 --> 01:09:17,079
