01:09:50,440 --> 01:09:51,599
All right.

922
01:09:51,600 --> 01:09:55,559
- Do you have another family?
- No. No, sweetheart. I didn't. Come on.

923
01:09:55,560 --> 01:09:56,919
<i>ZOOEY: Do you have another family?</i>

924
01:09:56,920 --> 01:09:58,079
