<i>- ETHAN: No.</i>

925
01:09:58,080 --> 01:10:00,079
<i>ZOOEY: Do you have another
perfect daughter somewhere?</i>

926
01:10:00,080 --> 01:10:02,119
Did you see me and not want me?

927
01:10:02,120 --> 01:10:04,721
